Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我改好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:12.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然速度也很驚人  但是真正讓我驚訝的是內容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,模糊不清的地方都進行了改善
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:19.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,無論何處都沒有衝突  全文條理清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這份做得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:21.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快去交給部長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒通過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是對方談到了公司的收支情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這些我們技術人員完全不懂的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以她根本無法招架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我對意志消沉的她說了這樣一句話
