Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明收下了好處  艾爾瑪還是沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:11.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她組建了工會  組織會議讓大家討論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拚盡全力呼籲改善工作環境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,令人意外的是  托爾居然在幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟順利的話  以後小林就能早點回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你可不要拖我的後腿啊  艾爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敵對勢力為了共同利益而一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都感覺或許能成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是  董事實在是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:43.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,運用道理和詭辯  將這些提議全部駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可惡  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:52.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣不是就趕不上去排車站前的限定點心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,理由居然是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,奇蹟般地完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趕上了限定點心的最後一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給我三個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,三個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給我兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給我兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一個就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃著好吃的點心度過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們想去野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,出遠門不能沒有大人陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她好像說了休息日也要上班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那托爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她給你寫了信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:54.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜看了求生電視節目之後  突然很想去山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我今天要去女僕咖啡廳幫忙所以不能陪她去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以麻煩你帶她們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我姑且還是信任你的  別讓我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾居然說她信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然有些居高臨下的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吧  我同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我帶你們去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了  康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就在這裡搭帳篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太是在去艾爾瑪大人家裡時在途中碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就叫他一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後呢  要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們租了釣竿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,康娜  我們要釣什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.02,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,亞馬遜森蚺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,釣魚啊  不禁讓人想起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:51.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也被釣過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我玩膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼辦法能快點釣到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,用手抓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再往那邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那邊有魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,釣到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我也喜歡往去那種地方鑽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖哩和飯也煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看來帶孩子也沒有很難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖哩真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  這蟲子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是毒蟲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也去放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我最近在研究能不能從龍脈裡汲取魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,山上有很強大的龍脈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男孩子都喜歡這種設定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,孩子們都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微不注意就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這點事都做不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對了  我會千里眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣就能馬上找到他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有人想從遠處偷窺我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定是露科亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她偶爾就會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有注意防範的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男孩子還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼  捕捉不到他們的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就不該找你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能會找不到回去的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為只是沿著龍脈走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原路返回就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以說男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們來之前好像沒跟艾爾瑪姐姐打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有沒有聽到什麼吼叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能是這附近有熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪姐姐不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因為我們隨意走動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她生我們的氣就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能是去找我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可惡  究竟去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:12:59.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跪拜求饒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒點用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:01.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幹啥啥不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好  你很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.13,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,但還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始  心中的托爾就一直在痛罵我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.84,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,又蠢又搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好  我在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有見到過幾個小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混蛋  你想被吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可惡  你們一個兩個都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,究竟在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,會去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:39.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:41.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之前在河邊看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可讓我擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:13:59.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼  是花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是為了艾爾瑪大人摘的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,送給你所以原諒我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好甜  原諒你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真好哄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是我在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天的花蜜我也吃得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,花蜜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我採的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.06,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這下你可不能覺得我可憐可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.10,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,大花  而且很香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可沒這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給你的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒蛋糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別蹬鼻子上臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天氣變熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為到夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.98,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}由於各種原因（艾爾瑪三昧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我向來不會答應調和勢力的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但這種暴力解決問題的方式我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這次看在你的份上  助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天我們採訪會移動的動物園ZOO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最有名的居然是傳聞中的長頸鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們來請教宮本園長幾個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪邀請託爾出來還真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,「最近身體變遲鈍了陪我出來活動活動筋骨」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:20.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,更加少見的是托爾居然就這麼答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,兩人之間的隔閡終於要消解了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,態度也都軟化了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定會以此為契機…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你太天真了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你覺得她為什麼會叫我們一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:44.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼時候停下來  由你來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身體哪裡遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,事到如今還想決出個勝負來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你能回到原來的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還沒死心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你還是很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在蠱惑人心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她嘴上說著主張調和  引導人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那不過是因為她所處的立場罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她也曾被人利用  遭人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:20.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在心底裡還是會與人類保持一定距離的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以現在依然懷疑托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我覺得不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:28.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我又沒想幹壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,壓根沒想過把人類怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過是保持了一定的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你就開心地在女僕咖啡廳和人類一起幹活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明以前態度上對人類毫不信任  不屑一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現在卻完全轉變過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在原來的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還不是把為人類所崇拜的我當傻子看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是被供奉了起來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,實際上你並沒接觸他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而一臉開心的樣子過於滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.83,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(957.333,919.333)\bord2\1a&H73&\c&H000000&\t(1000,1250,\bord0)\t(1249,1250\c&H000000&\1a&H00&)\t(1000,1521,\blur10)}「把他們當作螞蟻看才對」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.83,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(957.333,919.333)\bord0\t(1249,1250,)\t(1000,1521,\be20)}「把他們當作螞蟻看才對」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但你現在吃的不再是獻上的供品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經可以自己買吃的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是那時的飯菜更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這才讓人無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,更好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你還不趕緊滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吃是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而你卻不知所蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那時聽說你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊  然後好不容易找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對我這麼冷淡卻和人類相談甚歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:53.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快變回以前那樣對我好點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:14.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但一碼歸一碼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我們一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給我做好覺悟吧  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是我這邊的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然已經看過好幾次龍的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也差不多習慣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看著令人安心
