Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你才要請吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
